    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法简介：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以德州扑克玩法为基础，每次行动时抽取额外的计策卡，通过透视底牌和敌方的扑克牌提前掌握信息，通过改变扑克牌的花色或者点数追求强大的牌型，在具有决定性优势时层层加码，赢得酣畅淋漓的胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--改变扑克牌点数：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037390/extras/2c5598c68d353dac00fca795bae062f8.avif?t=1738649573\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--游戏中的特殊牌型：五条</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037390/extras/3bb8fc22ea150786fa5a9b9241eaceca.avif?t=1738649573\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037390/extras_big/3bb8fc22ea150786fa5a9b9241eaceca.avif?t=1738649573 width=800 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--胜利后选择最合适的技能击败对手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037390/extras/1efbafd9cbca6e037dbeeccb4b3f0331.avif?t=1738649573\" width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事简介：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无垠的荒漠之中，零星分布着十座城市群，每座城市群的中心，万丈白玉柱擎举着一颗光芒万丈的太阳，为人类提供生存所必须的光和热。随着「后羿射日」的陌生故事再次现世，青城的太阳突发爆炸！世界发生了翻天覆地的变化，真相又到底是什么？通过不断积累计策、收集秘密，战胜对手、发掘真相！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037390/extras/f0b51afb02a2db062217f108062c2610.avif?t=1738649573\" width=800 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike简介：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市上空的太阳突发爆炸，将你的城市夷为废墟，你侥幸逃过一劫，世界却已经沦为炼狱，你需要不断充实自己的实力，在充满恶意的世界中不断维生……</p>",
